---
title: Chargrilled Peri Peri Pork & Creamy Corn Slaw with Cheesy Chorizo & Roast Potato Toss
description: If you can’t beat the heat then we say join in with this mild peri peri sauced pork. Spicing things up again is a chorizo
baked and grilled alongside barbecued veggies, then finished off with smoked Cheddar. If it’s getting a little too hot in
here, we recommend cooling your pallet down with an aioli corn salsa.
